It begins near the Missouri Pacific Railroad two miles southwest of Angleton in central Brazoria County and runs thirty-two miles south and then northeast, through Cox Lake, Lost Lake, the Gulf Intracoastal Canal, and Bastrop Bayqqv to its mouth on Christmas Bay, in east central Brazoria County.
